nodes.title: GNPS-Untargeted metabolomics on samples from a genetic mouse model of Primary Sclerosing Cholangitis (PSC).
nodes.description: Liver, ileum, cecum, colon, serum, feces, and bile juice samples were collected from the 36 mice.  MS/MS data acquisition was carried out on a Thermo Q Exactive mass spectrometer in positive ionization mode, with chromatographic separation achieved using a Phenomenex Polar C18 column.
